{"tid":1827164,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳華府施壓在美生產軍用晶片 台積電回應了","createTime":"2020-01-16T17:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T17:55:29.000Z","uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2f6201697e410d1c542790a281dd6538dc3257f6","tid":1827164,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T17:32:53.000Z","msg":"傳華府施壓在美生產軍用晶片 台積電回應了<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/6735127/article-%E5%82%B3%E8%8F%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%96%BD%E5%A3%93%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E8%BB%8D%E7%94%A8%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87-%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E4%BA%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F6735127%2Farticle-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2596%25BD%25E5%25A3%2593%25E5%259C%25A8%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2594%25A2%25E8%25BB%258D%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2599%25B6%25E7%2589%2587-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%25A9%258D%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E4%25BA%2586%2F&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcykBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=e9fead2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/6735127/article-%E5%82%B3%E8%8F%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%96%BD%E5%A3%93%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E8%BB%8D%E7%94%A8%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87-%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E4%BA%86/</a><br />\n<br />\n日媒報導，華府正加強施壓台積電赴美國生產軍用晶片。台積電表示，公司從未排除在美國設廠生產的可能性，只是目前尚無具體計畫，將依客戶需求考量。<br />\n<br />\n「日經亞洲評論」報導引述一名台灣政府高官說法指出，基於國家安全考量，美國政府希望應用於軍事計畫的晶片，能在美國本土製造，美國不打算退讓。<br />\n<br />\n台積電表示，不理解報導為何聲稱美國政府施壓。公司從未排除赴美國設廠生產的可能性，只是目前還沒有具體計畫。<br />\n<br />\n去年10月紐約時報就曾報導，美國軍方為維持軍事優勢，打算請台積電在美國設廠。台積電董事長劉德音也曾說，台積電沒有直接受到來自美國國防部的壓力，不過，美國客戶確實有受到美國國防部的關心，希望國防相關產品能在美國生產。<br />\n<br />\n劉德音表示，在美國設廠生產，服務與成本都是挑戰，不過，台積電要幫客戶解決競爭力與國防安全問題。台積電強調，將會依客戶需求考量。"},{"pid":"bbabc45333ccad75fb6f8c6bb81d54e9c58d4efa","tid":1827164,"uid":83251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T17:47:49.000Z","msg":"其實佢一直都向美國有分公司"},{"pid":"3d649bd572733a068c189444ef3c0263897a47fd","tid":1827164,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T17:52:24.000Z","msg":"喂TSM畀錢你賺呀！賺唔賺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTSM:賺囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d7e8a21d99fe3349c38e3150d0e34fa160cb968","tid":1827164,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T17:54:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"968de1f9e967d3905343871f5b03a756ff9f67ff","tid":1827164,"uid":58413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T17:55:22.000Z","msg":"軍用晶片佢咪賣貴d囉。"},{"pid":"33271ea3df72bc8f9a7cdd28e3785086a4aeba43","tid":1827164,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T17:55:29.000Z","msg":"根本成間公司既靈魂都來自美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}